This is guide with scripts to facilitate the installation of an OCP KNI virtual machine as the and to deploy baremetal masters and workers. 

Based on 
https://docs.openshift.com/container-platform/4.8/installing/installing_bare_metal_ipi/ipi-install-installation-workflow.html

Prequisites: To run the provisioner as a VM, the nested virtualization is required to be enabled. Also 2 virtual bridges, for baremetal and provisioning.

